- **âš¡ Simplified Imports**: Access all core layout components including sizers through the main apiwx package
- **ðŸ›¡ï¸ Robust Multiton Pattern**: Enhanced Multiton mixin with improved `__del__` fallback handling for base UI classes without destructor attributes
- **ðŸ”’ Memory Management**: Added safe destruction handling for Multiton instances with proper cleanup and error prevention

